  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Humanitarian action of the Sri Lankan Navy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan Navy recovered the damaged Rameswaram fishing boat along with the fishermen in the middle of the sea.",
        "This humanitarian act of the Sri Lankan Navy has won appreciation not only among the fishermen of Rameswaram but also among the fishermen of Tamil Nadu.",
        "Last Saturday (30), fishermen from Rameswaram fishing harbor in more than 400 boats went to the sea to fish after getting fishing permits.",
        "At around 11 o'clock on Saturday night, due to a malfunction in the engine of one of the boats, sea water started entering the boat and the boat slowly started sinking into the sea.",
        "Noticing this, the Sri Lankan Navy patrolling the area immediately rescued the fishermen safely.",
        "In this case, the Sri Lankan Navy personnel dragged the damaged boat to the international sea border and safely handed over the fishermen and the boat to the boat sent by the owner of the boat.",
        "The Sri Lankan Navy provided full assistance to the 6 fishermen in the boat which broke down in the middle of the sea and sent them back to Rameswaram safely.",
        "The incident of feeding the fishermen of Tamil Nadu whose boat broke down in the Sri Lankan waters and sending them back safely has created resilience not only among the fishermen of Rameswaram but also among the fishermen of Tamil Nadu. (a)"
      ],
